</span></p><p class='default'>
Default value: <p><code>localhost</code></p>
</p></dd><dt><a class='title-link' name='port' href='#port'></a> port</dt><dd><p class='desc'><span class='type'>(<span class='integer'>integer</span>)</span><span class='required'>(Optional)</span><span class='description'><p>The port Sonarr is running on.</p>
